{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":560,"text":"Have you ever heard the one\nabout how breastfeeding is free?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":5266,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":6440,"text":"Yeah, it's pretty funny,"},{"time":8680,"text":"because it's only free if we don't value\nwomen's time and energy."},{"time":15120,"text":"Any mother can tell you\nhow much time and energy it takes"},{"time":19720,"text":"to liquify her body --"},{"time":21680,"text":"to literally dissolve herself --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":24240,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":25840,"text":"as she feeds this precious\nlittle cannibal."}]},{"cues":[{"time":29120,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":31360,"text":"Milk is why mammals suck."},{"time":35400,"text":"At Arizona State University,"},{"time":37320,"text":"in the Comparative Lactation Lab,"},{"time":39280,"text":"I decode mothers' milk composition"},{"time":42080,"text":"to understand its complexity"},{"time":45080,"text":"and how it influences infant development."},{"time":48720,"text":"The most important thing that I've learned"},{"time":51800,"text":"is that we do not do enough\nto support mothers and babies."},{"time":57720,"text":"And when we fail mothers and babies,"},{"time":59920,"text":"we fail everyone\nwho loves mothers and babies:"},{"time":64080,"text":"the fathers, the partners,\nthe grandparents, the aunties,"},{"time":67280,"text":"the friends and kin\nthat make our human social networks."},{"time":72480,"text":"It's time that we abandon\nsimple solutions and simple slogans,"},{"time":77240,"text":"and grapple with the nuance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":80200,"text":"I was very fortunate"},{"time":81800,"text":"to run smack-dab\ninto that nuance very early,"},{"time":85480,"text":"during my first interview\nwith a journalist"},{"time":88560,"text":"when she asked me,"},{"time":89880,"text":"\"How long should a mother\nbreastfeed her baby?\""},{"time":96040,"text":"And it was that word \"should\"\nthat brought me up short,"},{"time":100640,"text":"because I will never tell a woman\nwhat she should do with her body."}]},{"cues":[{"time":106800,"text":"Babies survive and thrive"},{"time":108600,"text":"because their mother's milk\nis food, medicine and signal."},{"time":113280,"text":"For young infants,"},{"time":114520,"text":"mother's milk is a complete diet"},{"time":116480,"text":"that provides all the building\nblocks for their bodies,"},{"time":119080,"text":"that shapes their brain"},{"time":120480,"text":"and fuels all of their activity."},{"time":123360,"text":"Mother's milk also feeds the microbes"},{"time":125800,"text":"that are colonizing\nthe infant's intestinal tract."},{"time":128840,"text":"Mothers aren't just eating for two,"},{"time":130560,"text":"they're eating for two to the trillions."},{"time":134560,"text":"Milk provides immunofactors\nthat help fight pathogens"},{"time":139000,"text":"and mother's milk provides hormones\nthat signal to the infant's body."}]},{"cues":[{"time":144800,"text":"But in recent decades,"},{"time":146320,"text":"we have come to take milk for granted."},{"time":148480,"text":"We stopped seeing\nsomething in plain sight."},{"time":151480,"text":"We began to think of milk as standardized,\nhomogenized, pasteurized,"},{"time":156640,"text":"packaged, powdered,\nflavored and formulated."},{"time":160680,"text":"We abandoned the milk of human kindness"},{"time":162880,"text":"and turned our priorities elsewhere."}]},{"cues":[{"time":166560,"text":"At the National Institutes of Health"},{"time":168320,"text":"in Washington DC"},{"time":169960,"text":"is the National Library of Medicine,"},{"time":172520,"text":"which contains 25 million articles --"},{"time":175280,"text":"the brain trust of life science\nand biomedical research."},{"time":180080,"text":"We can use keywords\nto search that database,"},{"time":183480,"text":"and when we do that,"},{"time":184760,"text":"we discover nearly a million\narticles about pregnancy,"},{"time":188640,"text":"but far fewer about\nbreast milk and lactation."},{"time":192840,"text":"When we zoom in on the number of articles\njust investigating breast milk,"},{"time":197480,"text":"we see that we know much more\nabout coffee, wine and tomatoes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":202000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":204520,"text":"We know over twice as much\nabout erectile dysfunction."}]},{"cues":[{"time":208240,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":212240,"text":"I'm not saying we shouldn't\nknow about those things --"},{"time":214840,"text":"I'm a scientist, I think\nwe should know about everything."},{"time":217560,"text":"But that we know so much less --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":219920,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":221720,"text":"about breast milk --"},{"time":223040,"text":"the first fluid a young mammal\nis adapted to consume --"},{"time":225840,"text":"should make us angry."},{"time":227960,"text":"Globally, nine out of 10 women will\nhave at least one child in her lifetime."},{"time":232480,"text":"That means that nearly 130 million\nbabies are born each year."},{"time":236960,"text":"These mothers and babies\ndeserve our best science."}]},{"cues":[{"time":241080,"text":"Recent research has shown\nthat milk doesn't just grow the body,"},{"time":244760,"text":"it fuels behavior\nand shapes neurodevelopment."},{"time":248800,"text":"In 2015, researchers discovered"},{"time":251840,"text":"that the mixture of breast milk\nand baby saliva --"},{"time":254840,"text":"specifically, baby saliva --"},{"time":256920,"text":"causes a chemical reaction\nthat produces hydrogen peroxide"},{"time":260760,"text":"that can kill staph and salmonella."},{"time":263880,"text":"And from humans and other mammal species,"},{"time":266080,"text":"we're starting to understand\nthat the biological recipe of milk"},{"time":269520,"text":"can be different when produced\nfor sons or daughters."},{"time":273560,"text":"When we reach for donor milk\nin the neonatal intensive care unit,"},{"time":277200,"text":"or formula on the store shelf,"},{"time":279200,"text":"it's nearly one-size-fits-all."},{"time":281960,"text":"We aren't thinking about how sons\nand daughters may grow at different rates,"},{"time":286240,"text":"or different ways,"},{"time":287480,"text":"and that milk may be a part of that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":290200,"text":"Mothers have gotten the message"},{"time":292160,"text":"and the vast majority of mothers\nintend to breastfeed,"},{"time":295600,"text":"but many do not reach\ntheir breastfeeding goals."},{"time":299520,"text":"That is not their failure;"},{"time":301640,"text":"it's ours."},{"time":303760,"text":"Increasingly common medical conditions\nlike obesity, endocrine disorders,"},{"time":308360,"text":"C-section and preterm births"},{"time":310000,"text":"all can disrupt the underlying\nbiology of lactation."},{"time":313280,"text":"And many women do not have\nknowledgeable clinical support."}]},{"cues":[{"time":317520,"text":"Twenty-five years ago,"},{"time":318920,"text":"the World Health Organization\nand UNICEF established criteria"},{"time":322800,"text":"for hospitals to be\nconsidered baby friendly --"},{"time":325400,"text":"that provide the optimal level\nof support for mother-infant bonding"},{"time":329240,"text":"and infant feeding."},{"time":331480,"text":"Today, only one in five babies\nin the United States"},{"time":334880,"text":"is born in a baby-friendly hospital."},{"time":339200,"text":"This is a problem,"},{"time":340480,"text":"because mothers can grapple\nwith many problems"},{"time":343360,"text":"in the minutes, hours, days\nand weeks of lactation."},{"time":347440,"text":"They can have struggles\nwith establishing latch,"},{"time":349960,"text":"with pain,"},{"time":351200,"text":"with milk letdown"},{"time":352440,"text":"and perceptions of milk supply."},{"time":355000,"text":"These mothers deserve\nknowledgeable clinical staff"},{"time":359520,"text":"that understand these processes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":362480,"text":"Mothers will call me as they're\ngrappling with these struggles,"},{"time":366880,"text":"crying with wobbly voices."},{"time":371400,"text":"\"It's not working."},{"time":373240,"text":"This is what I'm supposed\nto naturally be able to do."},{"time":375920,"text":"Why is it not working?\""},{"time":378240,"text":"And just because something\nis evolutionarily ancient"},{"time":381840,"text":"doesn't mean that it's easy\nor that we're instantly good at it."},{"time":385560,"text":"You know what else\nis evolutionarily ancient?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":388240,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":392200,"text":"Sex."},{"time":393520,"text":"And nobody expects us\nto start out being good at it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":396480,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":399480,"text":"Clinicians best deliver\nquality equitable care"},{"time":404040,"text":"when they have continuing education"},{"time":406080,"text":"about how to best support\nlactation and breastfeeding."},{"time":409840,"text":"And in order to have\nthat continuing education,"},{"time":412080,"text":"we need to anchor it\nto cutting-edge research"},{"time":414240,"text":"in both the life sciences\nand the social sciences,"},{"time":417760,"text":"because we need to recognize"},{"time":419480,"text":"that too often"},{"time":421640,"text":"historical traumas and implicit biases"},{"time":425080,"text":"sit in the space between\na new mother and her clinician."},{"time":429680,"text":"The body is political."},{"time":432760,"text":"If our breastfeeding support\nis not intersectional,"},{"time":436480,"text":"it's not good enough."},{"time":439120,"text":"And for moms who have to return for work,"},{"time":442120,"text":"because countries like the United States\ndo not provide paid parental leave,"},{"time":447160,"text":"they can have to go back in as short\nas just a few days after giving birth."}]},{"cues":[{"time":452400,"text":"How do we optimize\nmother and infant health"},{"time":455760,"text":"just by messaging\nabout breast milk to moms"},{"time":459120,"text":"without providing\nthe institutional support"},{"time":461920,"text":"that facilitates\nthat mother-infant bonding"},{"time":464600,"text":"to support breastfeeding?"},{"time":466680,"text":"The answer is: we can't."},{"time":471000,"text":"I'm talking to you, legislators,"},{"time":473480,"text":"and the voters who elect them."},{"time":475440,"text":"I'm talking to you, job creators\nand collective bargaining units,"},{"time":480160,"text":"and workers, and shareholders."},{"time":483360,"text":"We all have a stake\nin the public health of our community,"},{"time":487320,"text":"and we all have a role\nto play in achieving it."},{"time":491200,"text":"Breast milk is a part\nof improving human health."},{"time":495000,"text":"In the NICU, when infants are born\nearly or sick or injured,"},{"time":499040,"text":"milk or bioactive constituents in milk\ncan be critically important."},{"time":503360,"text":"Environments or ecologies,"},{"time":504800,"text":"or communities where there's\nhigh risk of infectious disease,"},{"time":508040,"text":"breast milk can be incredibly protective."},{"time":510520,"text":"Where there are emergencies\nlike storms and earthquakes,"},{"time":514159,"text":"when the electricity goes out,"},{"time":515679,"text":"when safe water is not available,"},{"time":517679,"text":"breast milk can keep babies\nfed and hydrated."},{"time":522360,"text":"And in the context of humanitarian crises,"},{"time":525080,"text":"like Syrian mothers fleeing war zones,"},{"time":528240,"text":"the smallest drops can buffer babies\nfrom the biggest global challenges."}]},{"cues":[{"time":535480,"text":"But understanding breast milk\nis not just about messaging to mothers"},{"time":540240,"text":"and policy makers."},{"time":542080,"text":"It's also about understanding\nwhat is important in breast milk"},{"time":545200,"text":"so that we can deliver better formulas"},{"time":548000,"text":"to moms who cannot or do not\nbreastfeed for whatever reason."},{"time":552440,"text":"We can all do a better job"},{"time":554280,"text":"of supporting the diversity\nof moms raising their babies"},{"time":557600,"text":"in a diversity of ways."}]},{"cues":[{"time":560680,"text":"As women around the world struggle"},{"time":562560,"text":"to achieve political,\nsocial and economic equality,"},{"time":566240,"text":"we must reimagine motherhood"},{"time":568800,"text":"as not the central,\ncore aspect of womanhood,"},{"time":574040,"text":"but one of the many potential facets\nof what makes women awesome."}]},{"cues":[{"time":579080,"text":"It's time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":581040,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}